      kicker: "Foundations",
      dek: `Your budget's three columns gave you a gap number. This chapter is about closing it — the three honest ways money actually reaches a short film, and why the least glamorous one funds the most films.`,
      seoTitle: "Short Film Grants & Funding: How to Pay for Your Short | Filmmaker Genius",
